»CL1:INFO&RULES
----------»
As you probably have surmised, this
text isn't too serious. Yep, that's
right it isn't, because this really is
a small, cozy, noncommercial party,
without network, internet or PC
Quakers. You'll have to get your own
fun, there'll be no non stop action
from us, there'll be no concerts, no
food to be bought at the partyplace,
no nothing, no facilities at all.. No
wait, that was not ENTIRELY correct..
You know, the partyplace is 5km
distant from the somewhat big town of
Grenå, where there's McDonalds (a
partyplace without McD, wouldn't be a
partyplace, now would it?), lotsa'
other things, and lotsa BEER! And
drugs too for that matter, hehe ;)
You're not completely stuck in Ålsø,
the boring partytown, with a
convenience store, and 2 inhabitants +
this school, so don't despair.. This
were the outside facilities.. Isn't
that cool?

Inside? Hmm, we have a hall at a
school, we have ELECTRICITY, we have
tables, we have SOME toilets I think
(don't you just LOOOVE thorough
planning? Heh), we have a little
chips/drink/etc. shop with NORMAL
prizes for you and then we have.. Uhmm
yes well. It's noncommercial! You'll
have to have fun without all the
crappy TP facilities hehe. But check           »PIC:Z1.iff»
the rules section later, for how you
may NOT have fun INSIDE atleast ;) And
now (tadaaaa).. The entrancefees! (and
